1. *Kratko* sam odgovorio na pitanje. (I answered the question briefly.)
2. Ona je *kratko* govorila o njemu. (She spoke briefly about him.)
3. On je *kratko* odgovorio. (He answered shortly.)
4. Poruka je *kratko* bila objašnjena. (The message was briefly explained.)
5. On nije *kratko* odgovorio. (He didn't answer shortly.)
6. Zašto je odgovor bio *kratko*? (Why was the answer brief?)
7. Ona je *kratko* odgovorila. (She answered shortly.)
8. *Kratko* smo porazgovarali. (We talked briefly.)